        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                "THE PAW PATROL TRICYCLE FOR CHILDREN COMES WITH UNIQUE DESIGN YOU WILL LOVE - Make the most out of your little ones' outdoor play time with this lovely Paw Patrol Fly Wheel Ride On Tricycle for kids. The amazing junior big wheel tricycle features a cute soft blue color and comes stylized with full color images of beloved Paw Patrol characters Chase, Rubble, Skye, and more. The Paw Patrol Rider Trike is designed to maintain stability and control.",
                "THE PAW PATROL FLY WHEELS IS PERFECT FOR KIDS WHO LOVE TRICYCLES - Every Nickelodeon fan will be thrilled to ride this cool Paw Patrol childrens tricycle at the park, on their backyard, and anywhere they go! It's the perfect gift for boys and girls who love to spend time with their friends and family watching their favorite shows and playing with outdoor riding toys for kids. Designed for safety and comfort, kids will ride the trike for hours.",
                "INCLUDED IN THE PURCHASE OF PAW PATROL RIDER TRICYCLE FOR KIDS - Includes 1 Paw Patrol Fly Wheels Junior Cruiser Ride-On Tricycle kids will love to ride for hours. The kids tricycle comes with full color images of cool Paw Patrol characters Chase, Rubble, Skye, Rocky and Marshall as stickers to be applied during assembly. It features a 10 inch front wheel designed for stability and control. Paw Patrol ride-on tricycle measures 14.25Wx14.5Hx23.5L.",
                "HIGH-QUALITY PAW PATROL KIDS BIG WHEELS TRYCICLE - The Nickelodeon Paw Patrol Junior Cruiser riding toy is made with high-quality, resistant, durable, and child-friendly materials that are meant to give your kids endless hours of fun riding the tricycle big wheel indoors and outdoors. It features easy-grip handle bars and a low center of gravity so your kid can ride in safety and style. Recommended for children ages 2 to 4.",
                "IDEAL USE FOR THE PAW PATROL BIG WHEEL TRICYCLE FOR GIRLS AND BOYS - Encourage your little ones to get outside and get rolling with this amazing Paw Patrol boys and girls Big Wheel Tricycle. Kids cruisers make the perfect gift for boys and girls who love spending time outdoors and riding along their parents and siblings. Boys and girls can ride the kiddy cruiser at the park, in the backyard, and bring them along vacations and family trips."
            ],
